Dustpan and brush set have a useful little loop for storing on a hook. That serves as a decoration when not in use.

Soft brush has two rows of natural horsehair bristles, very dense, the edge of dustpan is tapered, catches the debris easily. Easy to hold and clean small places with.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Hostess or Housewarming gift
reviews.reviewText: This has become my go-to for hostess or housewarming gift. My friends don’t need extra stuff. Consumables are lovely, but this is special. Beautifully made, meaningful in terms of supporting people who are visually impaired, truly useful for coffee ground/sugar/flour spills, and small enough to be easily stowed. Alone as a hostess gift, or with a couple of teas and jams as a housewarming gift; it is hard to go wrong with this set as a gift.
